                .card-body
                  | When you get in touch with us, we set up a 45-60 minute consultation that is at no cost to you.
            .card.ts-accrodion-01
              #step02.card-header
                h5.mb-0
                  button.ts-btn.btn-lg.w-100.text-left(
                    data-toggle="collapse" 
                    data-target="#step02Content" 
                    aria-expanded="false" 
                    aria-controls="step02Content") Define what advice you are looking for
              #step02Content.collapse(
                aria-labelledby="step02" 
                data-parent="#process")
                .card-body
                  | When you get in touch with us, we set up a 45-60 minute consultation that is at no cost to you.
            .card.ts-accrodion-01
              #step03.card-header
                h5.mb-0
                  button.ts-btn.btn-lg.w-100.text-left(
                    data-toggle="collapse" 
                    data-target="#step03Content" 
                    aria-expanded="false" 
                    aria-controls="step03Content") A plan to help you achieve your goals
              #step03Content.collapse(
                aria-labelledby="step03" 
                data-parent="#process")
                .card-body
                  | After we have met, your financial adviser will develop a plan based on all the information they have collected from you.
            .card.ts-accrodion-01
                #step04.card-header
                  h5.mb-0
                    button.ts-btn.btn-lg.w-100.text-left(
                      data-toggle="collapse" 
                      data-target="#step04Content" 
                      aria-expanded="false" 
                      aria-controls="step04Content") Present your plan and answer any questions
                #step04Content.collapse(
                  aria-labelledby="step04" 
                  data-parent="#process")
                  .card-body
                    | After about two weeks, your financial adviser will be in touch to present their findings and recommendations and go into.
            .card.ts-accrodion-01
                #step05.card-header
                  h5.mb-0
                    button.ts-btn.btn-lg.w-100.text-left(
                      data-toggle="collapse" 
                      data-target="#step05Content" 
                      aria-expanded="false" 
                      aria-controls="step05Content") Present your plan and answer any questions
                #step05Content.collapse(
                  aria-labelledby="step05" 
                  data-parent="#process")
                  .card-body
                    | After about two weeks, your financial adviser will be in touch to present their findings and recommendations and go into.

  .home-01-teams.bg--whitesmoke.pd-carousel-focus
    .ts-overlay
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          .ts-section-heading-01.align-center.heading-carousel-focus
            h2 The Great Team
      
      .carousel.align-center-items.arrows-intro.dots-theme.carousel-focus(
        data-items="3"
        data-items-md="2"
        data-items-sm="1"
        data-items-xs="1" 
        data-margin="40"
        data-center="true"
        data-dots="false"
        data-arrows="true" 
        data-autoplay='false' 
        data-hoverpause="true"
        data-autoplay-timeout="9000"
        data-loop="true")
